title: Ellen's Stardust Diner
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Has vegan choices such as shepherd's pie, pastas, salads, desserts. A fun retro 1950s theme diner filled with nostalgic memorabilia. Watch 1950s videos on authentic 1956 Predicta televisions and drive-in theatre screen. Unique diner also features a singing waitstaff and variety shows. Loud atmosphere due to singing and customers applauding. Free Wi-Fi.
